  "detailed_description": "Crafting Block World is an adventure with sandbox elements that will help you build your ideal world!<br><br><strong>ENDLESS WORLD!</strong><br>Explore the vast block world full of mysteries and interesting places! Endless plains, dense forest, dark caves — your adventures know no boundaries! Find a comfortable place and start building!<br><br><strong>CITY BUILDING GAMES!</strong><br>You are not limited in resources and can build anything from the simplest houses to huge and luxurious castles! Construction of houses, huts, castles, penthouses — embody your most insane ideas, because craft is not limited!",
